---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="AI PM 必備證照指南：2025 年最值得考的 5 張 AI 證照 — AI PM INSIDER" description="AI 產品經理必備證照完整比較：iPAS AI 應用規劃師、Microsoft AI Product Manager、Google AI Essentials、Google Cloud Digital Leader、PMP AI 改版。費用、難度、適合誰一次看懂。">

  <!-- JSON-LD: FAQPage -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "AI 產品經理需要考什麼證照？",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "AI PM 最推薦的證照組合：台灣考 iPAS AI 應用規劃師（經濟部官方認證），國際考 Microsoft AI Product Manager Professional Certificate（微軟 × Coursera 聯合推出，直接對標 AI PM 職能）。如果想補強基礎，Google AI Essentials 是快速入門的好選擇。" }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "非技術背景可以考哪些 AI 證照？",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "iPAS AI 應用規劃師初級不需要程式背景，考的是 AI 概念理解與應用規劃能力，非常適合 PM、行銷、商業分析師。Microsoft AI Product Manager 和 Google AI Essentials 也偏重應用與策略，不要求寫 code。" }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "AI 證照對產品經理求職加薪有幫助嗎？",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "有。iPAS 證照受台灣企業認可，部分企業提供考取加薪或補助；Microsoft 和 Google 的證照在國際求職市場上是明確的能力證明。PMP 2025 年改版加入 AI 題型，更是 PM 圈含金量最高的管理證照。" }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <!-- JSON-LD: BreadcrumbList -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "首頁", "item": Astro.site?.toString() },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "AI PM 證照指南", "item": new URL("/ai-certifications", Astro.site).toString() }
    ]
  })} />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-12 md:pb-16 overflow-hidden bg-white">
    <div class="site-container px-6 relative z-10">

      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-light-subtle text-sm font-body mb-8 md:mb-10 hover:text-brand-accent-dark transition-colors">
        <iconify-icon icon="solar:arrow-left-linear" class="text-lg"></iconify-icon>
        <span>返回首頁</span>
      </a>

      <div class="mb-10 md:mb-14">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-brand-light-subtle text-xs tracking-widest font-body uppercase mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <div class="w-8 h-px bg-brand-accent-dark"></div>
          <span>AI PM Certification Guide</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-brand-light-text mb-4 md:mb-6">
          AI PM <span class="text-brand-accent-dark">必備證照指南</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-brand-light-subtle font-body leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          想成為 AI 產品經理，該從哪張證照開始？精選 5 張最適合 PM 的 AI 證照，從台灣到國際、從入門到進階，幫你規劃最有效的學習路徑。
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-4 md:mt-6 flex-wrap">
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs bg-brand-accent-dark/10 text-brand-accent-dark rounded-full font-body">PM 視角精選</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs bg-purple-600/10 text-purple-600 rounded-full font-body">台灣 + 國際</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs bg-emerald-600/10 text-emerald-600 rounded-full font-body">非技術友善</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison Table -->
  <section class="relative pb-16 md:pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-white">
    <div class="site-container px-6 relative z-10">

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-brand-light-text mb-6 md:mb-8">
        一覽比較
      </h2>

      <!-- Desktop Table -->
      <div class="hidden md:block overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm font-body border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b-2 border-brand-accent-dark/20">
              <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-heading font-semibold text-brand-light-text">證照</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-heading font-semibold text-brand-light-text">發照單位</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-heading font-semibold text-brand-light-text">難度</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-heading font-semibold text-brand-light-text">費用</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-heading font-semibold text-brand-light-text">語言</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 font-heading font-semibold text-brand-light-text">適合誰</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 font-heading font-semibold text-brand-light-text">形式</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-brand-light-subtle">
            <tr class="border-b border-brand-light-border">
              <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-semibold text-brand-light-text">iPAS AI 應用規劃師</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">經濟部</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4"><span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded text-xs">入門</span></td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">NT$ 1,500</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">中文</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">PM、行銷、轉職者</td>
              <td class="py-4">線下考試</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-brand-light-border">
              <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-semibold text-brand-light-text">Microsoft AI Product Manager</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">Microsoft × Coursera</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4"><span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded text-xs">中階</span></td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">約 US$ 49/月</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">英文</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">AI PM、產品經理</td>
              <td class="py-4">線上課程</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-brand-light-border">
              <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-semibold text-brand-light-text">Google AI Essentials</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">Google × Coursera</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4"><span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded text-xs">入門</span></td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">約 US$ 49/月</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">英文（有字幕）</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">所有非技術角色</td>
              <td class="py-4">線上課程</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-brand-light-border">
              <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-semibold text-brand-light-text">Google Cloud Digital Leader</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">Google</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4"><span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded text-xs">中階</span></td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">US$ 99</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">英文 / 中文</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">PM、商業決策者</td>
              <td class="py-4">線上考試</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-brand-light-border">
              <td class="py-4 pr-4 font-semibold text-brand-light-text">AWS AI Practitioner</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">Amazon</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4"><span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded text-xs">入門</span></td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">US$ 75</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">英文 / 中文</td>
              <td class="py-4 pr-4">PM、商業分析師</td>
              <td class="py-4">線上考試</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Mobile Cards -->
      <div class="md:hidden space-y-4">
        <div class="border border-brand-light-border rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text">iPAS AI 應用規劃師</h3>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded text-xs shrink-0">入門</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-1.5 text-xs font-body text-brand-light-subtle">
            <span>發照單位</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">經濟部</span>
            <span>費用</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">NT$ 1,500</span>
            <span>語言</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">中文</span>
            <span>適合誰</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">PM、行銷、轉職者</span>
            <span>形式</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">線下考試</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-brand-light-border rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text">Microsoft AI Product Manager</h3>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded text-xs shrink-0 ml-2">中階</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-1.5 text-xs font-body text-brand-light-subtle">
            <span>發照單位</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">Microsoft × Coursera</span>
            <span>費用</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">約 US$ 49/月</span>
            <span>語言</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">英文</span>
            <span>適合誰</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">AI PM、產品經理</span>
            <span>形式</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">線上課程</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-brand-light-border rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text">Google AI Essentials</h3>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded text-xs shrink-0 ml-2">入門</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-1.5 text-xs font-body text-brand-light-subtle">
            <span>發照單位</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">Google × Coursera</span>
            <span>費用</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">約 US$ 49/月</span>
            <span>語言</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">英文（有字幕）</span>
            <span>適合誰</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">所有非技術角色</span>
            <span>形式</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">線上課程</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-brand-light-border rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text">Google Cloud Digital Leader</h3>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded text-xs shrink-0 ml-2">中階</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-1.5 text-xs font-body text-brand-light-subtle">
            <span>發照單位</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">Google</span>
            <span>費用</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">US$ 99</span>
            <span>語言</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">英文 / 中文</span>
            <span>適合誰</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">PM、商業決策者</span>
            <span>形式</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">線上考試</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-brand-light-border rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text">AWS AI Practitioner</h3>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded text-xs shrink-0 ml-2">入門</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-1.5 text-xs font-body text-brand-light-subtle">
            <span>發照單位</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">Amazon</span>
            <span>費用</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">US$ 75</span>
            <span>語言</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">英文 / 中文</span>
            <span>適合誰</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">PM、商業分析師</span>
            <span>形式</span><span class="text-brand-light-text">線上考試</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detail Cards -->
  <section class="relative pb-16 md:pb-20 bg-gray-50/50">
    <div class="site-container px-6 relative z-10 pt-12 md:pt-16">

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-brand-light-text mb-8 md:mb-10">
        各證照詳細介紹
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-8 md:space-y-10">

        <!-- Card 1: iPAS -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-6 md:p-8 pb-0 flex-wrap">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl gold-gradient flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-heading font-bold text-sm">1</span>
            </div>
            <div class="min-w-0">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-light-text">iPAS AI 應用規劃師</h3>
              <span class="text-xs text-brand-light-subtle font-body">經濟部 ・ 台灣</span>
            </div>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded-full text-xs font-body font-medium sm:ml-auto">台灣首選 ・ CP 值最高</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8 space-y-5">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text mb-2">考什麼</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-light-subtle font-body leading-relaxed">
                初級分兩科：（1）人工智慧基礎概論 — AI 定義與分類、資料處理、機器學習、生成式 AI；（2）生成式 AI 應用與規劃 — No Code/Low Code 工具、導入評估與風險管理。全選擇題，各科 50 題。
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text mb-2">為什麼 PM 該考這張</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-brand-light-subtle font-body leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                <li>台灣唯一政府級 AI 證照，企業 HR 認得</li>
                <li>不用寫 code，考的是 AI 規劃能力 — PM 的核心價值</li>
                <li>費用最低（NT$1,500），2-4 週可準備</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text mb-2">Angela 觀點</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-light-subtle font-body leading-relaxed italic">
                「如果你在台灣，這張是投資報酬率最高的第一步。不用寫 code、費用低、政府背書，考的正是企業最缺的 AI 應用規劃能力。先拿這張打底，再往國際證照進攻。」
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Highlighted CTA -->
          <div class="ipas-cta-banner mx-6 md:mx-8 mb-6 md:mb-8 rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FEF2F2, #FEE2E2, #FEF2F2);">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #EF4444 0, #EF4444 1px, transparent 0, transparent 50%); background-size: 12px 12px;"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <iconify-icon icon="solar:star-bold" class="text-red-500 text-lg"></iconify-icon>
                <span class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-red-600">本站免費備考資源</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-light-text font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
                50 篇白話教學 + 模擬題庫，用生活化比喻與圖解帶你從零基礎一次考過。
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <a href="/ipas" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 gold-gradient text-white font-heading font-semibold rounded-full text-xs no-underline transition-transform hover:scale-105">
                  <iconify-icon icon="solar:book-bold" class="text-sm"></iconify-icon>
                  50 篇免費教學
                </a>
                <a href="/exam" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-white border border-brand-accent-dark/30 text-brand-accent-dark font-heading font-semibold rounded-full text-xs no-underline transition-transform hover:scale-105">
                  <iconify-icon icon="solar:document-text-bold" class="text-sm"></iconify-icon>
                  模擬題庫
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Microsoft AI PM -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-6 md:p-8 pb-0 flex-wrap">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl gold-gradient flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-heading font-bold text-sm">2</span>
            </div>
            <div class="min-w-0">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-light-text">Microsoft AI Product Manager</h3>
              <span class="text-xs text-brand-light-subtle font-body">Microsoft × Coursera ・ 國際</span>
            </div>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-xs font-body font-medium sm:ml-auto">最對標 AI PM</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8 space-y-5">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text mb-2">學什麼</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-light-subtle font-body leading-relaxed">
                微軟官方推出的 AI 產品經理專業證照課程，涵蓋：AI 產品策略、使用者需求與 AI 能力匹配、負責任的 AI 設計、AI 產品生命週期管理、利害關係人溝通，以及如何將 AI 功能落地為產品。
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text mb-2">為什麼 PM 該考這張</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-brand-light-subtle font-body leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                <li>全球唯一「AI Product Manager」命名的證照</li>
                <li>微軟品牌背書，LinkedIn 上辨識度高</li>
                <li>課程內容直接對標 AI PM 日常工作</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text mb-2">準備資源</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-light-subtle font-body leading-relaxed">
                Coursera 線上課程，可自由安排進度，約 3-4 個月完成。訂閱制約 US$ 49/月，完成後獲得 Professional Certificate。
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm text-brand-light-text mb-2">Angela 觀點</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-light-subtle font-body leading-relaxed italic">
                「這張是目前市場上最正宗的 AI PM 證照。如果你想在履歷上直接寫『Microsoft Certified AI Product Manager』，沒有比這張更對口的了。英文授課是門檻，但也是加分項。」
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Google AI Essentials -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-border rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-6 md:p-8 pb-0 flex-wrap">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl gold-gradient flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <span class="text-white font-heading font-bold text-sm">3</span>
            </div>
            <div class="min-w-0">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-light-text">Google AI Essentials</h3>
              <span class="text-xs text-brand-light-subtle font-body">Google × Coursera ・ 國際</span>
            </div>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded-full text-xs font-body font-medium sm:ml-auto">最快入門</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8 space-y-5">
            <div>
